Media, LLC, part of Springer Nature.

DOI: 10.1007/978-1-0716-2209-4_23
PMID: 35819776 [Indexed for MEDLINE]


81. BMJ Open Diabetes Res Care. 2022 Jul;10(4):e002738. doi: 
