Applications of CRISPR-Cas9 as an Advanced Genome Editing System in Life 
Sciences.

Tavakoli K(1), Pour-Aboughadareh A(2), Kianersi F(3), Poczai P(4), Etminan A(5), 
Shooshtari L(5).

Author information:
(1)Department of Medical Laboratory Science, Kermanshah Branch, Islamic Azad 
