Exploratory analysis using machine learning of predictive factors for falls in 
type 2 diabetes.

Suzuki Y(1), Suzuki H(2), Ishikawa T(3), Yamada Y(3), Yatoh S(4), Sugano Y(4), 
Iwasaki H(4), Sekiya M(4), Yahagi N(4), Hada Y(5), Shimano H(4)(6)(7)(8).
